<template>
  <body>
    
  </body>
    <script type="module">
      import Typebot from 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@typebot.io/js@0.2.22/dist/web.js'
    
      Typebot.initPopup({
        typebot: "diagnostico-horas",
        apiHost: "https://tbchat.dourasoft.com.br",
        autoShowDelay: 0,
      });
    </script>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    name: 'HelloHome',
    //class="flex flex-colums, "
    props: {
      // Definindo props para possíveis usos futuros
      title: {
        type: String,
        default: 'Hello Home'
      }
    }
  }
  </script>
  
  <style scoped>
  .hello-home {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .hello-home h1 {
    font-size: 2em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: #333;
  }
  </style>
